874
00:31:30,950 --> 00:31:31,590
right?

875
00:31:31,610 --> 00:31:32,820
The police haven't filed a case yet.

876
00:31:32,820 --> 00:31:33,670
This is

877
00:31:33,670 --> 00:31:34,290
how the organization

878
00:31:34,290 --> 00:31:36,440
takes care of Liu Gang in his best interest.

879
00:31:36,440 --> 00:31:37,270
Take care of?

880
00:31:39,480 --> 00:31:40,570
All these years,

881
00:31:41,150 --> 00:31:42,910
have you ever taken care of us?

882
00:31:44,250 --> 00:31:45,650
Liu Gang has worked on the front line

883
00:31:45,650 --> 00:31:47,760
for more than ten years!

884
00:31:48,390 --> 00:31:49,270
At this age,

885
00:31:49,300 --> 00:31:51,360
he still works hard on the mountain!

886
00:31:52,470 --> 00:31:54,570
Maybe he hasn't made any contributions,

887
00:31:54,570 --> 00:31:56,440
but he has always played a part in it.

888
00:31:56,440 --> 00:31:57,090
Yes.

889
00:31:57,870 --> 00:31:59,270
Juan, actually...

890
00:32:00,650 --> 00:32:01,400
I talked

891
00:32:01,440 --> 00:32:02,840
to Liu Gang before.

892
00:32:02,850 --> 00:32:03,420
I said

893
00:32:03,910 --> 00:32:04,990
he could report to the leaders, right?

894
00:32:04,990 --> 00:32:06,250
To get himself transferred from the front line.

895
00:32:06,250 --> 00:32:07,160
He refused.

896
00:32:07,200 --> 00:32:08,390
That's easy for you to say!

897
00:32:08,390 --> 00:32:09,250
Our whole family

898
00:32:09,250 --> 00:32:11,780
are relying on him to make money to support us!

899
00:32:11,880 --> 00:32:13,210
Calm down, Lijuan.

900
00:32:13,410 --> 00:32:14,740
They'll take care of it.

901
00:32:15,110 --> 00:32:18,010
He is the only breadwinner in my family.

902
00:32:19,630 --> 00:32:21,060
As his wife,

903
00:32:21,330 --> 00:32:23,050
I don't have much income.

904
00:32:25,840 --> 00:32:26,470
Why are you sitting on the floor?

905
00:32:26,470 --> 00:32:27,670
There are stools.

906
00:32:32,170 --> 00:32:33,080
Use it as a cushion.

907
00:32:33,080 --> 00:32:33,950
Don't sit on the floor.

908
00:32:33,950 --> 00:32:34,830
No.

909
00:32:36,750 --> 00:32:37,710
I just want

910
00:32:38,420 --> 00:32:40,740
him to make more money on the front line.

911
00:32:42,050 --> 00:32:43,900
If you lay him off,

912
00:32:44,380 --> 00:32:46,610
how can we support our lives?

913
00:32:48,190 --> 00:32:51,640
My parents are still sick now.

914
00:32:52,230 --> 00:32:53,980
No one would do such a thing

915
00:32:54,440 --> 00:32:56,300
if they lead a rich life!

916
00:32:58,960 --> 00:33:00,910
Alright, stop crying.

917
00:33:01,330 --> 00:33:03,130
Crying won't solve the problem.

918
00:33:06,320 --> 00:33:07,030
Dahai,

919
00:33:07,700 --> 00:33:09,400
why don't you defer your decision?

920
00:33:09,400 --> 00:33:10,730
Expelling him from the factory is such a big deal.

921
00:33:10,730 --> 00:33:12,790
Why don't you discuss it again?

922
00:33:12,810 --> 00:33:13,740
What do you know?

923
00:33:13,750 --> 00:33:15,250
Discuss?

924
00:33:15,750 --> 00:33:16,390
Liu Gang didn't make mistakes

925
00:33:16,390 --> 00:33:17,450
for the first time!

926
00:33:17,790 --> 00:33:19,840
Do you forget what happened last year?

927
00:33:19,840 --> 00:33:20,650
How could you forget

928
00:33:20,650 --> 00:33:22,470
that someone got severely injured and ended up in the hospital?

929
00:33:22,470 --> 00:33:23,970
The factory has made a decision!

930
00:33:23,970 --> 00:33:25,760
It's not my own decision!

931
00:33:26,050 --> 00:33:26,800
Zero tolerance for it!

932
00:33:26,800 --> 00:33:27,730
He must be fired!

933
00:33:28,710 --> 00:33:31,240
Then I'll go to the factory manager tomorrow!

934
00:33:31,260 --> 00:33:32,100
I'll let everyone see

935
00:33:32,100 --> 00:33:32,960
how badly we end

936
00:33:32,960 --> 00:33:34,290
because of the factory!

937
00:33:34,580 --> 00:33:35,660
-Lijuan. -Lijuan.

938
00:33:35,720 --> 00:33:36,670
Lijuan, you should keep your temper under control,

939
00:33:36,670 --> 00:33:37,340
all right?

940
00:33:37,920 --> 00:33:39,120
Your bad temper

941
00:33:39,150 --> 00:33:41,510
has something to do with the poor condition of your family!

942
00:33:41,510 --> 00:33:42,530
Stop it.

943
00:33:46,770 --> 00:33:47,740
What should I do?

944
00:33:49,150 --> 00:33:50,970
[Linqi No.2 High School Registration Form for Students Late to School]

945
00:33:51,150 --> 00:33:51,820
Ms. Han,

946
00:33:51,900 --> 00:33:53,430
please sign your name here.

947
00:33:58,020 --> 00:33:59,420
Okay, thank you, Ms. Han.

948
00:34:04,380 --> 00:34:05,080
Thank you.

949
00:34:07,000 --> 00:34:08,460
Come with me to the office.

950
00:34:12,650 --> 00:34:13,580
Yuan Shanqing,

951
00:34:13,830 --> 00:34:15,570
you've been constantly late to school

952
00:34:15,570 --> 00:34:16,630
so many times

953
00:34:16,670 --> 00:34:18,130
since the school started.

954
00:34:18,310 --> 00:34:20,190
Did anything happen at home?

955
00:34:20,320 --> 00:34:21,560
Or,

956
00:34:21,739 --> 00:34:22,469
do you

957
00:34:22,469 --> 00:34:24,070
experience any discomfort?

958
00:34:24,750 --> 00:34:25,420
No.

959
00:34:25,800 --> 00:34:27,330
I hope you can tell me directly

960
00:34:27,330 --> 00:34:28,860
if anything happens to you,

961
00:34:29,100 --> 00:34:30,980
so that I can know how to help you.

962
00:34:32,659 --> 00:34:35,290
I won't be late again.

963
00:34:35,510 --> 00:34:36,440
I always said

964
00:34:36,469 --> 00:34:37,750
I wanted to pay a home visit,

965
00:34:37,750 --> 00:34:38,949
but you didn't agree.

966
00:34:39,090 --> 00:34:41,949
Now you're constantly late, saying nothing happened.

967
00:34:41,949 --> 00:34:43,090
In your student information form,

968
00:34:43,090 --> 00:34:44,469
the information about your parents is empty,

969
00:34:44,469 --> 00:34:46,520
and so are your parents' phone numbers.

970
00:34:46,520 --> 00:34:47,440
I know.

971
00:34:48,110 --> 00:34:51,370
Your family is experiencing some special circumstances.

972
00:34:51,949 --> 00:34:52,790
But I really

973
00:34:52,830 --> 00:34:54,090
want to help you.

974
00:34:54,790 --> 00:34:55,630
Ms. Han,

975
00:34:57,260 --> 00:34:59,180
my family is quite normal.

976
00:35:00,120 --> 00:35:00,850
I promise

977
00:35:00,880 --> 00:35:02,080
I won't be late again.

978
00:35:02,990 --> 00:35:04,320
Did anyone in your class

979
00:35:04,320 --> 00:35:05,730
bully you?

980
00:35:07,280 --> 00:35:08,010
No.

981
00:35:17,150 --> 00:35:19,260
[Wanted Criminal]

982
00:35:24,040 --> 00:35:25,770
Luo Zheng, you've gone too far!

983
00:35:31,020 --> 00:35:31,780
Have I?

984
00:35:32,210 --> 00:35:33,470
You're a class leader.

985
00:35:34,020 --> 00:35:34,630
Given what you've done,

986
00:35:34,630 --> 00:35:35,430
other classmates

987
00:35:35,430 --> 00:35:36,890
will only look down on you.

988
00:35:39,870 --> 00:35:41,810
I can quit being a class leader.

989
00:36:19,060 --> 00:36:20,720
Get ready for the class first.

990
00:36:31,480 --> 00:36:32,550
Where did you have your hair cut?

991
00:36:32,550 --> 00:36:33,670
It looks great.

992
00:36:34,670 --> 00:36:35,730
It's cool this way.

993
00:36:35,760 --> 00:36:36,910
You've gone too far.

994
00:36:36,940 --> 00:36:37,800
You're so mean.

995
00:36:37,800 --> 00:36:38,490
Yeah.

996
00:36:38,520 --> 00:36:39,720
Stop crying.

997
00:36:39,880 --> 00:36:40,840
Stop crying.

998
00:36:41,120 --> 00:36:42,240
You're so mean.

999
00:36:42,280 --> 00:36:43,500
You're so mean.

1000
00:36:43,540 --> 00:36:44,570
Exactly.

1001
00:36:45,090 --> 00:36:47,370
Well, what do you mean?

1002
00:36:47,400 --> 00:36:48,220
As if my whole family

1003
00:36:48,220 --> 00:36:49,320
bullied your family.

1004
00:36:49,320 --> 00:36:50,350
Your dad bullied us!

1005
00:36:50,350 --> 00:36:51,810
Your dad must see himself great!

1006
00:36:51,810 --> 00:36:53,060
He can fire anyone at his will!

1007
00:36:53,060 --> 00:36:54,680
How did my dad bully you?

1008
00:36:54,760 --> 00:36:56,040
He bullied us!

1009
00:36:56,070 --> 00:36:57,230
You, stop shouting.

1010
00:36:58,350 --> 00:36:59,690
And you, don't be like this.

1011
00:36:59,690 --> 00:37:01,930
Well, what he said is ridiculous.

1012
00:37:01,960 --> 00:37:03,230
My dad bullied your family?

1013
00:37:03,230 --> 00:37:04,870
How could your dad get fired if he hadn't made mistakes?

1014
00:37:04,870 --> 00:37:06,310
Don't you know what your dad did?

1015
00:37:06,310 --> 00:37:07,990
Li Si, stop it.

1016
00:37:08,310 --> 00:37:09,180
Under this circumstance,

1017
00:37:09,180 --> 00:37:10,720
what's the point of saying this?

1018
00:37:10,720 --> 00:37:11,780
Sit down. Sit down.

1019
00:37:11,880 --> 00:37:14,230
His father is the only breadwinner in his family.

1020
00:37:14,230 --> 00:37:15,780
How can they carry on with their lives?

1021
00:37:15,780 --> 00:37:17,200
How can he get the chance to go to school?

1022
00:37:17,200 --> 00:37:18,240
That's right.

1023
00:37:20,030 --> 00:37:20,750
Why don't you

1024
00:37:20,750 --> 00:37:21,630
talk to your dad after you're home?

1025
00:37:21,630 --> 00:37:22,580
He's really pitiful.

1026
00:37:22,580 --> 00:37:23,980
His mother has no income.

1027
00:37:26,360 --> 00:37:27,580
Stop looking!

1028
00:37:27,600 --> 00:37:29,180
Go back to your classes!

1029
00:37:29,620 --> 00:37:30,680
Alright. Alright.

1030
00:37:32,090 --> 00:37:32,850
Go back to your seats.

1031
00:37:32,850 --> 00:37:34,030
Stop looking. Stop looking.

1032
00:37:34,030 --> 00:37:34,920
All right. All right.

1033
00:37:34,920 --> 00:37:36,810
There will be a way out.

1034
00:37:48,490 --> 00:37:49,530
Where do you live?

1035
00:37:52,350 --> 00:37:53,280
North District.

1036
00:37:55,000 --> 00:37:56,350
It's not that far.

1037
00:37:58,510 --> 00:38:00,140
But I often see you late to school.

1038
00:38:00,140 --> 00:38:00,750
Is it because...

1039
00:38:00,750 --> 00:38:01,950
I won't be late again.

1040
00:38:08,820 --> 00:38:10,460
There's a sentence

1041
00:38:10,630 --> 00:38:11,430
from a book I read before,

1042
00:38:11,430 --> 00:38:12,340
saying

1043
00:38:12,890 --> 00:38:14,730
a real strong person

1044
00:38:14,760 --> 00:38:16,070
does not care about the dirty tricks...

1045
00:38:16,070 --> 00:38:17,100
-Of rats. -Thank you.

1046
00:38:17,100 --> 00:38:17,900
I'm fine.

1047
00:38:39,820 --> 00:38:40,630
I'm sorry.

1048
00:38:52,940 --> 00:38:55,700
[Wanted Criminal]

1049
00:38:57,560 --> 00:38:59,620
Give me another bowl of soup, please.

1050
00:39:00,990 --> 00:39:01,790
Well,

1051
00:39:02,480 --> 00:39:03,160
our factory

1052
00:39:03,190 --> 00:39:04,960
has never fired anyone.

1053
00:39:06,540 --> 00:39:07,400
It has to be subject to

1054
00:39:07,400 --> 00:39:08,650
the rules.

1055
00:39:09,550 --> 00:39:11,100
Or what should Dahai do?

1056
00:39:11,590 --> 00:39:12,350
Now,

1057
00:39:12,350 --> 00:39:13,830
everyone

1058
00:39:13,830 --> 00:39:14,450
scolds Dahai instead.

1059
00:39:14,450 --> 00:39:16,170
It's not fair, right?

1060
00:39:17,260 --> 00:39:18,470
In my view,

1061
00:39:18,620 --> 00:39:19,540
the factory

1062
00:39:19,560 --> 00:39:20,640
is getting worse.

1063
00:39:21,310 --> 00:39:23,140
What should you do if that's the case?

1064
00:39:23,140 --> 00:39:24,670
You can't steal oil, right?

1065
00:39:25,510 --> 00:39:27,060
Just because each factory doesn't do well,

1066
00:39:27,060 --> 00:39:28,780
everyone should do evil?

1067
00:39:30,120 --> 00:39:31,180
Well, in your view,

1068
00:39:31,950 --> 00:39:34,010
does anything happen to the factory?

1069
00:39:34,170 --> 00:39:35,630
I heard that several units

1070
00:39:35,870 --> 00:39:37,800
have advanced the retirement age.

1071
00:39:37,880 --> 00:39:39,640
What's their intention behind this?

1072
00:39:39,640 --> 00:39:41,220
Do they want us to retire early

1073
00:39:41,220 --> 00:39:42,340
without earning too much money?

1074
00:39:42,340 --> 00:39:44,080
Don't listen to the stupid gossip

1075
00:39:44,080 --> 00:39:45,780
or spread it.

1076
00:39:46,240 --> 00:39:47,000
I didn't.

1077
00:39:47,030 --> 00:39:48,450
I'm just talking to you.

1078
00:39:50,710 --> 00:39:51,970
Do you hear what I said?

1079
00:39:52,300 --> 00:39:53,100
I'm full.

1080
00:39:54,560 --> 00:39:56,120
You're going to be unable to have adequate meals.

1081
00:39:56,120 --> 00:39:57,940
Come on, study harder.

1082
00:39:59,330 --> 00:40:00,480
I can't eat anymore as well.

1083
00:40:00,480 --> 00:40:03,140
Let's use it to make porridge tomorrow morning.

1084
00:40:04,100 --> 00:40:05,070
You two...

1085
00:40:05,650 --> 00:40:07,250
Don't listen to your mother.

1086
00:40:08,100 --> 00:40:08,910
After dinner,

1087
00:40:08,940 --> 00:40:10,810
go back to your room and do your homework.

1088
00:40:10,810 --> 00:40:12,540
I'll have to be on duty tonight.

1089
00:40:20,510 --> 00:40:21,790
Liu Junbao in my class

1090
00:40:21,790 --> 00:40:22,670
cried all day.

1091
00:40:23,420 --> 00:40:24,440
Li Si was scolded because of this.

1092
00:40:24,440 --> 00:40:26,300
What does it have to do with him?

1093
00:40:26,470 --> 00:40:27,350
It makes him

1094
00:40:27,370 --> 00:40:29,170
become an evil son of some landlord all of a sudden.

1095
00:40:29,170 --> 00:40:30,320
He's just like Yuan Shanqing

1096
00:40:30,320 --> 00:40:31,120
in your class.

1097
00:40:36,410 --> 00:40:39,210
What they can only do is hit someone when he's down.

1098
00:40:39,280 --> 00:40:40,150
What does adults' business

1099
00:40:40,150 --> 00:40:41,610
have to do with their kids?

1100
00:40:42,210 --> 00:40:44,540
When one family member becomes a wanted criminal,

1101
00:40:44,540 --> 00:40:45,280
the whole family

1102
00:40:45,280 --> 00:40:47,010
seem to have committed a crime.

1103
00:40:47,560 --> 00:40:48,890
You mean Yuan Shanqing?

1104
00:40:53,190 --> 00:40:53,830
Dad.

1105
00:40:54,150 --> 00:40:55,280
Where is sandpaper?

1106
00:40:55,670 --> 00:40:57,330
You may find it in the toolbox.

1107
00:41:01,080 --> 00:41:02,870
Why do you need sandpaper?

1108
00:41:41,040 --> 00:41:42,170
I still need 30 yuan.

1109
00:41:42,830 --> 00:41:44,090
I really have no money.

1110
00:41:45,310 --> 00:41:46,480
Where are your parents?

1111
00:41:46,480 --> 00:41:47,650
Ask them to come quickly.

1112
00:41:47,650 --> 00:41:48,560
Miss,

1113
00:41:48,650 --> 00:41:50,410
can you give my sister an injection first?

1114
00:41:50,410 --> 00:41:50,970
Please.

1115
00:41:51,000 --> 00:41:52,600
I'll make up for it tomorrow.

1116
00:41:54,520 --> 00:41:55,400
I'm sorry.

1117
00:41:55,430 --> 00:41:56,870
I'm not allowed to do it.

1118
00:41:56,990 --> 00:41:58,790
Go and borrow money from others.

1119
00:41:59,470 --> 00:42:00,310
Okay.

1120
00:42:00,640 --> 00:42:01,720
I'll do it now.

1121
00:42:04,710 --> 00:42:05,670
What happened?

1122
00:42:07,440 --> 00:42:08,890
Can you lend me 30 yuan?

1123
00:42:08,950 --> 00:42:09,650
Now.

1124
00:42:20,360 --> 00:42:22,240
Hu didn't jump off the bridge.

1125
00:42:22,490 --> 00:42:23,500
But her mother did

1126
00:42:23,530 --> 00:42:24,730
without hesitation.

1127
00:42:25,080 --> 00:42:27,080
It was the first time we had realized

1128
00:42:27,540 --> 00:42:28,140
adults

1129
00:42:28,160 --> 00:42:30,490
would also experience so many sad things.

1130
00:42:30,490 --> 00:42:31,400
I know

1131
00:42:31,430 --> 00:42:33,360
they are digesting them silently.

1132
00:42:33,820 --> 00:42:34,440
We can make many choices

1133
00:42:34,440 --> 00:42:35,560
in our lives.

1134
00:42:36,180 --> 00:42:37,380
But there's one thing

1135
00:42:37,660 --> 00:42:39,140
we can never choose.

1136
00:42:40,210 --> 00:42:42,270
What kind of family we'll be born into

1137
00:42:42,350 --> 00:42:44,260
and what kind of parents we'll have

1138
00:42:44,260 --> 00:42:45,720
are not what we can decide.

1139
00:42:47,120 --> 00:42:47,840
Back then,

1140
00:42:47,880 --> 00:42:48,870
there was no such word

1141
00:42:48,870 --> 00:42:50,270
called original family.

1142
00:42:50,590 --> 00:42:51,070
But

1143
00:42:51,090 --> 00:42:52,030
if parents

1144
00:42:52,030 --> 00:42:53,880
can't be their air-raid shelter,

1145
00:42:53,880 --> 00:42:55,160
every danger

1146
00:42:55,190 --> 00:42:56,430
will bring gunfire.

1147
00:42:57,230 --> 00:42:58,500
Many people

1148
00:42:59,060 --> 00:43:00,520
will spend their lifetime

1149
00:43:00,950 --> 00:43:01,870
healing those wounds

1150
00:43:01,870 --> 00:43:03,870
caused by the gunfire.
